    <h1 class="c-heading c-heading--lg">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="c-article__body">

      <p>This is my personal website. I respect your privacy and want to be upfront about what data is involved when you visit. No legalese — just a plain explanation of how things work.</p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>I use <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong> to understand how people use this site — things like which pages get visited and what countries visitors come from. Cloudflare collects this data on the server side through request logs. It doesn't use cookies or track you across the web, but it does process standard request information like your IP address, browser type, and the pages you visit. Cloudflare uses this data to provide me with aggregate statistics and does not sell it or use it for advertising.</p>

      <h2>Fonts</h2>
      <p>This site loads typefaces from <strong>Google Fonts</strong>. When your browser requests these fonts, Google receives your IP address and standard connection information. Google's <a href="https://developers.google.com/fonts/faq/privacy">font privacy policy</a> states that this data is not used for tracking or combined with other Google services.</p>

      <h2>Newsletter</h2>
      <p>If you sign up for my newsletter, I collect your email address through <strong>Kit</strong> (formerly ConvertKit). Your email is stored by Kit and used only to send you the newsletter. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in every email. I won't sell or share your email with anyone.</p>

      <h2>Embedded content</h2>
      <p>Some posts may include embedded content from third-party services like YouTube, CodePen, or social media platforms. These embeds may set their own cookies and collect data according to their own privacy policies. This only happens on the specific posts that contain those embeds — not across the site.</p>

      <h2>Local storage</h2>
      <p>This site uses your browser's local storage (not cookies) to remember your preferences — things like your preferred color theme, text size, and line height. This data stays on your device and is never sent to me or anyone else. You can clear it any time through your browser settings.</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>This site does not set any cookies. Cloudflare's CDN may set a minimal cookie for security and performance purposes (such as bot detection). These are not used for tracking or advertising.</p>

      <h2>Your data</h2>
      <p>If you've given me your email through the newsletter signup and want it removed, you can unsubscribe directly or email me and I'll take care of it. If you have any questions about how your data is handled, I'm happy to help.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For any privacy-related questions, reach out at <a href="mailto:privacy@plasticmind.com">privacy@plasticmind.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>I may update this policy as the site evolves. Any changes will be posted here.</p>

      <p>Last updated: March 25, 2026.</p>

    </div>

    {% include "partials/end-mark.njk" %}

